 used to search for them. Other farmers from the area assisted in the search. The police helicopter managed to locate one of the suspects near the scene, it is presumed that he died in the gunfire exchange. One of the firearms stolen in the farm attack, a hunting rifle, was recovered on the veranda of the farmhouse. Police are investigating the attack and death of the suspect. Read the original article in Afrikaans onÂ Maroela Media 